title: #92Noon! 10a Hour 2/9 - Biggs/Hester/NDN
description: Most of the hour is all about the greatness of Bears KR/WR Devin Hester, as he waits to hear if he's made the Hall of Fame. Brad Biggs from the Chicago Tribune opens things with his opinions on making the case for HOF. News to finish the hour.
